Package: makeJAGSmask
Type: Package
Title: Construct a Habitat Matrix for Use with SECR Analysis in JAGS or BUGS
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-06-28
Imports: MASS, abind, plotrix, raster
Suggests: secr, sp, rgeos
Author: Mike Meredith
Maintainer: Mike Meredith <mmeredith@wcs.org>
Description: Functions to create habitat masks for spatially explicit capture-recapture (SECR) analysis in BUGS or JAGS. This is done by converting a mask prepared by the \pkg{secr} package or a habitat raster.
License: GPL-3
NeedsCompilation: no